<docs>
   <doc for="ColorMap">
 <summary>
    Defines a map for converting colors.
 </summary>
 <remarks>
    This class defines a mapping between
    existing colors and the new colors to which they are to be converted. When the
    map is applied, any pixel of the old color is converted to the new color.
 </remarks>
   </doc>
   <doc for="ColorMap.ColorMap">
 <summary>
    <para>
       Initializes a new instance of the <see cref='System.Drawing.Imaging.ColorMap'/> class.
    </para>
 </summary>
   </doc>
   <doc for="ColorMap.OldColor">
 <summary>
    <para>
       Specifies the existing <see cref='System.Drawing.Color'/> to be
       converted.
    </para>
 </summary>
   </doc>
   <doc for="ColorMap.NewColor">
 <summary>
    <para>
       Specifes the new <see cref='System.Drawing.Color'/> to which to convert.
    </para>
 </summary>
   </doc>
</docs>

